Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.85,0:01:39.27,Default,,0,0,0,,WHO CAUSED THE FIRE?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.83,0:01:41.88,Default,,0,0,0,,What's up, John?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.48,0:01:43.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Try harder!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.34,0:01:48.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Can't you be faster than Lassie?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.81,0:01:50.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.84,0:01:51.89,Default,,0,0,0,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.81,0:01:55.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah... ah...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.36,0:01:56.69,Default,,0,0,0,,- Ah...!\N- Ah...!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.65,0:02:03.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Lassie went too far...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.71,0:02:30.15,Default,,0,0,0,,What's up, Duocho?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.77,0:02:31.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.81,0:02:35.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it our guest while I sleep?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.44,0:02:38.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.22,0:02:39.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Lassie!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.55,0:02:41.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this the big dog yours?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.85,0:02:42.91,Default,,0,0,0,,That's true, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.14,0:02:44.27,Default,,0,0,0,,What about you Uncle?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.33,0:02:49.97,Default,,0,0,0,,The road was divided into four\Ndirections, and while I was thinking
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.00,0:02:51.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I was sleepy and I fall asleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.34,0:02:51.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.90,0:02:58.85,Default,,0,0,0,,And now...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.02,0:03:01.22,Default,,0,0,0,,We have guests!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.59,0:03:02.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Guests?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.66,0:03:05.07,Default,,0,0,0,,We are not guests!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.95,0:03:07.51,Default,,0,0,0,,That's too bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.64,0:03:08.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't it, Duocho?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.30,0:03:12.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Very bad!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.94,0:03:14.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Doucho is very sad,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.12,0:03:16.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}his chest is almost bursting with pain!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.35,0:03:19.98,Default,,0,0,0,,So one of you will come and ease his grief!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.82,0:03:30.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh...!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.35,0:03:37.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Just awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.32,0:03:40.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.21,0:03:49.42,Default,,0,0,0,,This is my partner!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.90,0:03:52.23,Default,,0,0,0,,This is my partner.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.22,0:03:56.03,Default,,0,0,0,,His name is Pace! His specialty\Nis moving the vehicle.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.92,0:03:58.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Rory!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.97,0:04:01.60,Default,,0,0,0,,By the way, do you know\Na delicious bakery in the village?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.70,0:04:03.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Bakery? Maybe that is...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.65,0:04:06.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I know, Uncle Rice's bakery is the best!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.30,0:04:06.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.99,0:04:07.89,Default,,0,0,0,,That's true!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.96,0:04:09.32,Default,,0,0,0,,He's helped by his daughter, Mary!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.34,0:04:10.99,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the best in the whole village!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.11,0:04:12.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Well I've decided!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.46,0:04:14.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I have a place to go today!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.43,0:04:15.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't it, Duocho?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.71,0:04:24.93,Default,,0,0,0,,We have finally finished!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.95,0:04:26.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, let's go for a walk\Nand have a drink together!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.98,0:04:33.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh? Do you still deliver goods at this time?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.39,0:04:35.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You work harder than we do!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.63,0:04:40.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.67,0:04:49.06,Default,,0,0,0,,John! Sandy!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.39,0:04:51.46,Default,,0,0,0,,And Lassie? What are they doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.53,0:05:11.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Lassie, isn't it amazing?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.50,0:05:13.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you do the same?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.27,0:05:23.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And now, next...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.98,0:05:26.60,Default,,0,0,0,,We need some help!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.94,0:05:27.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.35,0:05:29.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.27,0:05:31.42,Default,,0,0,0,,This gentle miss, what do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.15,0:05:34.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah! Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.23,0:05:36.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Would your husband be reluctant to look at you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.93,0:05:38.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm rude!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.29,0:05:42.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Stay there and hold this!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.20,0:05:45.09,Default,,0,0,0,,So?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.26,0:05:46.46,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the best place!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.62,0:05:47.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, Doucho!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.52,0:06:00.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Ladies and gentlemen, this is\Nthe great partner of the spotlight!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.16,0:06:02.28,Default,,0,0,0,,And this gentle miss,\NI hope you applaud them!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.70,0:06:06.81,Default,,0,0,0,,And now, folks,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.81,0:06:08.90,Default,,0,0,0,,you have the honor to see some of my work!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.09,0:06:11.92,Default,,0,0,0,,We have utensils and all kinds of pans!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.22,0:06:13.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go! Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.11,0:06:20.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Good! Good!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.75,0:06:23.32,Default,,0,0,0,,You're welcome, thank you for your purchase!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.45,0:06:25.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I want this one.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.27,0:06:28.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Rory is doing business and\Nis traveling around England!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.88,0:06:30.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Me too I wish I would go to many places!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.71,0:06:31.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.28,0:06:33.11,Default,,0,0,0,,My God! My God! My God!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.22,0:06:35.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I would forget something important!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.49,0:06:37.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Please buy me bread to eat at dinner!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.03,0:06:38.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay! Lassie!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.19,0:06:41.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go! To the bakery!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.52,0:06:43.23,Default,,0,0,0,,You are! You are!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.78,0:06:46.34,Default,,0,0,0,,How can you leave your job like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.28,0:06:50.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm sorry!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.53,0:06:52.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Today there is no bread because all were sold!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.34,0:06:54.27,Default,,0,0,0,,- Not even one?\N- No!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.78,0:06:57.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll bake a new batch tomorrow morning...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.88,0:06:59.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I understood, there is none.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.83,0:07:01.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you have bread for tonight?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.39,0:07:02.13,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.22,0:07:04.28,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not for me, it is for Rory!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.31,0:07:05.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Rory?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.52,0:07:07.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, that man who has a dog\Nwhich does amazing movements?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.06,0:07:10.46,Default,,0,0,0,,His voice is so loud that\NI can hear him from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.57,0:07:14.21,Default,,0,0,0,,He came to this village because I told\Nhim that we have a delicious bakery.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.33,0:07:14.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.00,0:07:15.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Mary!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.75,0:07:17.15,Default,,0,0,0,,We don't have anything to sell!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.15,0:07:18.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Let him go!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.54,0:07:19.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.62,0:07:22.51,Default,,0,0,0,,But will that man stay here tonight?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.74,0:07:23.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Mary!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.71,0:07:26.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Tomorrow morning I'll give you fresh bread!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.74,0:07:27.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.82,0:07:30.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.83,0:07:32.62,Default,,0,0,0,,That's too bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.88,0:07:36.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Fresh bread makes the hearts of people happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.34,0:07:39.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Next to that beautiful girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.69,0:07:42.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I will work tomorrow!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.20,0:07:43.59,Default,,0,0,0,,But what will you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.69,0:07:45.30,Default,,0,0,0,,You have no house here!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.79,0:07:48.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing like that, I don't have\Na house at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.11,0:07:51.33,Default,,0,0,0,,So, will you sleep in the stable?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.45,0:07:53.38,Default,,0,0,0,,No no, but I'm a vagabond!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.53,0:07:55.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Displacement is wonderful!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.15,0:07:57.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Under the stars of the sky that seem to fall!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.50,0:08:00.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Towards that sky to the large galaxies!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.19,0:08:01.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I sleep under it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.10,0:08:03.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't it, Duocho?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.92,0:08:06.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Sky and stars...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.58,0:08:16.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Look like they really fall down!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.46,0:08:18.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Somehow this is scary...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.44,0:08:19.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.24,0:08:22.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you traveled in many places?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.88,0:08:23.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.44,0:08:26.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Just, almost.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.66,0:08:32.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Manchester, Glasgow, Newcastle,\Nand also Liverpool.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.22,0:08:34.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh...?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.53,0:08:38.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I only went to the simple villages.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.95,0:08:43.00,Default,,0,0,0,,My father was like me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.90,0:08:46.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I was used to staying out at night\Nand homeless,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.65,0:08:51.38,Default,,0,0,0,,but there are many people who are bored\Nto stay between the walls of the house.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.33,0:08:56.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Yet within this dimly lit window is a family.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.32,0:09:02.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Thinking about it, this is warm and gentle.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.89,0:09:05.34,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems that staying in a home\Nis a lot more better than this.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.26,0:09:10.89,Default,,0,0,0,,But Uncle Rice is always angry\Nand screaming loudly!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.58,0:09:12.71,Default,,0,0,0,,It's no good!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.84,0:09:14.51,Default,,0,0,0,,You should not say that!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.67,0:09:15.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.94,0:09:19.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Look!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.73,0:09:21.94,Default,,0,0,0,,It's Sandy!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.19,0:09:31.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Can't you smell the delicious things?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.93,0:09:42.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Pace, it's delicious! It's the truth!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.91,0:09:44.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh really? Oh really?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.46,0:09:46.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh really! Really really!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.99,0:09:49.68,Default,,0,0,0,,But there is a problem with\Nthe handle of this pot.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.85,0:09:53.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It can be used again after\Nit has been well repaired.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.98,0:09:57.35,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems that Sandy's mother is interested\Nin keeping the dishes well!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.43,0:09:58.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.17,0:09:59.94,Default,,0,0,0,,This pot is mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.97,0:10:00.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.63,0:10:03.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I got it from my deceased grandmother\Nwhen I was a little girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.14,0:10:04.71,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why I cared about it well!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.15,0:10:08.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it you who made this tasty soup...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.58,0:10:09.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.56,0:10:12.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that right? I apologize for my insolence!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.09,0:10:15.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Finally I knew! Isn't it, Duocho?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.99,0:10:21.72,Default,,0,0,0,,What now are natural people?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.78,0:10:23.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Haven't you seen a falling star\Nor something like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.43,0:10:25.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.26,0:10:26.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Oh!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.54,0:10:28.66,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a falling star!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.85,0:10:30.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh? Where? Where? Where?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.94,0:10:32.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Just gone...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.23,0:10:33.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I saw it too!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.47,0:10:36.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I really saw it! That is the devil... I am...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.23,0:10:44.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hm!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.72,0:10:48.15,Default,,0,0,0,,They made a fire in such a place!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.24,0:10:50.89,Default,,0,0,0,,What if a fire starts because of that? Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.82,0:10:53.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, kids, have to go back!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.95,0:10:54.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh...?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.68,0:10:56.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Although we enjoy being with you...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.48,0:11:00.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you have mothers and\Na warm home waiting for you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.59,0:11:02.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Children have specific times\Nand can't go out at night.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.99,0:11:05.31,Default,,0,0,0,,You are not like me, homeless!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.78,0:11:07.11,Default,,0,0,0,,See you tomorrow!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.25,0:11:09.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you have amazing\Nthings for tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.99,0:11:14.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Doucho wants to make this happen\Nwith greater success!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.88,0:11:16.42,Default,,0,0,0,,- Bye!\N- Good night!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.44,0:11:16.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.25,0:11:18.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Lassie, let's go!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.86,0:11:25.33,Default,,0,0,0,,That boy owns a huge dog,\Nbeautiful shape, Doucho.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.28,0:11:26.99,Default,,0,0,0,,It was good!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.23,0:11:48.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I have finished, Doucho.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.71,0:11:49.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Should I sleep now?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.77,0:12:44.91,Default,,0,0,0,,That's bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.15,0:12:52.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.37,0:12:55.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.70,0:12:57.37,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.40,0:12:59.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! It's a fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.35,0:13:01.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Wake up!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.78,0:13:05.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh? A fire started?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.00,0:13:07.85,Default,,0,0,0,,It's near my house!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.31,0:13:08.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.26,0:13:11.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Water! Water! Curse it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.50,0:13:16.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Give it to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.91,0:13:28.05,Default,,0,0,0,,It's bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.09,0:13:34.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.93,0:13:37.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Sandy!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.97,0:13:39.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I came to deliver the milk!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.18,0:13:41.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello, good morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.41,0:13:43.41,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Have you brought milk?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.02,0:13:45.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Unfortunately,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.33,0:13:47.13,Default,,0,0,0,,it's not from my house!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.21,0:13:51.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen, Mr. Rory needs milk with\Nthe bread at breakfast, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.06,0:13:52.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, that 's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.87,0:13:56.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Lassie, do you want to meet Dousho as well?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.60,0:14:00.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Who came this early morning?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.72,0:14:02.69,Default,,0,0,0,,- Colin?\N- Uh...!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.72,0:14:03.97,Default,,0,0,0,,John! Something bad happened!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.07,0:14:07.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Rory! Rory has troubles!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.16,0:14:08.44,Default,,0,0,0,,- Eh?\N- What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.01,0:14:14.03,Default,,0,0,0,,- Oh?\N- Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.85,0:14:24.36,Default,,0,0,0,,How many times should I tell you that?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.46,0:14:27.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I certainly turned off the fire before I slept!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.09,0:14:29.34,Default,,0,0,0,,So how it burned, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.37,0:14:30.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, Mr Rice...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.94,0:14:34.69,Default,,0,0,0,,This man worked hard to extinguish the fire.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.83,0:14:36.80,Default,,0,0,0,,What is important is that the fire\Ndidn't reached the nearby houses.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.80,0:14:39.77,Default,,0,0,0,,What will you do if we can't control the fire?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.90,0:14:43.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I also asked for help without any charge!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.11,0:14:45.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't think you will leave safely\Nafter you have caused the fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.40,0:14:47.08,Default,,0,0,0,,What will you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.64,0:14:48.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Father!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.73,0:14:50.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Dad, you always do this!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.04,0:14:54.22,Default,,0,0,0,,You are very interested in your customers\Nto buy bread from our home!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.22,0:14:55.69,Default,,0,0,0,,This guy is...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.72,0:14:56.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't joke with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.86,0:14:59.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I bake bread for the villagers only!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.00,0:15:03.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't sell to men of this kind!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.14,0:15:05.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Father!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.07,0:15:06.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.13,0:15:09.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know anything about bread,\Nbut it was hard to extinguish the fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.76,0:15:10.95,Default,,0,0,0,,This means
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.02,0:15:14.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I must preserve my life and\Nthe life of the people of my village.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.70,0:15:17.36,Default,,0,0,0,,It is better to leave our village immediately!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.80,0:15:19.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you have an objection?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.46,0:15:22.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll tell you again.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.83,0:15:24.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't set fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.30,0:15:27.03,Default,,0,0,0,,No, no doubt it's you!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.15,0:15:30.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I understand.  I don't like\Nto say this again though.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.91,0:15:32.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Scum...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.01,0:15:34.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I know that, you don't have to tell me that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.18,0:15:37.39,Default,,0,0,0,,You see? Definitely the reason!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.20,0:15:43.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to say only one thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.65,0:15:47.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I sell bowls and dishes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.22,0:15:53.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I travel to make people smile through\Nthe acrobatic games that Doucho loves.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.75,0:15:54.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.06,0:16:00.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Rory!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.87,0:16:01.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you leaving?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.03,0:16:03.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I have no other chioce.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.22,0:16:05.23,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.38,0:16:07.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't say "but" again!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.91,0:16:08.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for the food!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.23,0:16:10.75,Default,,0,0,0,,The food was delicious, miss!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.52,0:16:14.76,Default,,0,0,0,,It's fixed!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.00,0:16:19.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, the store owner wants me\Nto leave, so the village be protected.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.57,0:16:22.72,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll meet again!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.73,0:16:36.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Rory... left...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.59,0:16:41.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know if the lamp\Nor wood caused th fire.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.33,0:16:43.94,Default,,0,0,0,,It was close to my house and\Nit almost burned because of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.03,0:16:45.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Father!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.41,0:16:46.28,Default,,0,0,0,,A lamp?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.81,0:16:47.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Or wood?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.93,0:16:48.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.16,0:16:51.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey Colin!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.47,0:16:53.37,Default,,0,0,0,,To the worst, John!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.94,0:16:55.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Should I hit the door only?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.12,0:17:00.80,Default,,0,0,0,,John, what to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.86,0:17:01.62,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.78,0:17:04.76,Default,,0,0,0,,You say what?  But Mr. Rice is scary
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.98,0:17:06.25,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.37,0:17:08.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr Rice, I'm sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.19,0:17:13.62,Default,,0,0,0,,What? I must bake the bread late today\Nwith the oven already cooled!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.80,0:17:14.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll go to bake again!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.05,0:17:17.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Quick! He's gone!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.09,0:17:18.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, Mr Rice!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.57,0:17:21.25,Default,,0,0,0,,What? I'm busy!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.27,0:17:22.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Not me, but Colin...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.80,0:17:26.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me... this, sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.23,0:17:28.19,Default,,0,0,0,,So I said, what?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.34,0:17:31.66,Default,,0,0,0,,John, tell him...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.00,0:17:33.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh...?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.09,0:17:35.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.88,0:17:37.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this the truth?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.23,0:17:37.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.20,0:17:40.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What do you say?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.53,0:17:43.83,Default,,0,0,0,,The lamp and firewood were\Nextinguished at 11 o'clock!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.85,0:17:44.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.70,0:17:45.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh...?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.41,0:17:48.95,Default,,0,0,0,,This means that Colin woke up\Nand looked at the window.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.98,0:17:51.47,Default,,0,0,0,,How come a child stays up until late at night?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.49,0:17:52.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.60,0:17:54.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I was trying to see the meteors...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.04,0:17:56.23,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.38,0:17:57.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Falling stars, you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.03,0:18:00.68,Default,,0,0,0,,If you talk loudly you will scare the children!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.17,0:18:01.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.02,0:18:05.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, Mr. Rory turned off the lamp.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.34,0:18:08.18,Default,,0,0,0,,And extinguished the fire with water.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.38,0:18:09.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.38,0:18:09.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.18,0:18:13.05,Default,,0,0,0,,This means that wasn't the cause of the fire.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.23,0:18:14.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.58,0:18:18.19,Default,,0,0,0,,If the cause of the fire is different\Nfrom that, then...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.83,0:18:37.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Enough, just hurry up!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.29,0:18:41.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Can't you go faster?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.20,0:18:43.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm deaf, you're distracted in driving!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.34,0:18:45.14,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.27,0:18:47.75,Default,,0,0,0,,What do I say to that man?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.77,0:18:49.25,Default,,0,0,0,,You must apologize to him!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.61,0:18:52.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought about the safety of the village.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.08,0:18:54.59,Default,,0,0,0,,If I say so...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.71,0:18:58.18,Default,,0,0,0,,No matter what you say,\Nit's your fault anyway!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.40,0:19:02.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I was very impressed by Rory's presence.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.91,0:19:03.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.81,0:19:06.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope he stays in our village\Nand doesn't go anywhere else.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.18,0:19:08.09,Default,,0,0,0,,That's too bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.73,0:19:13.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to talk more with Mr. Rory.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.87,0:19:25.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't make this sad face, Duocho!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.64,0:19:28.44,Default,,0,0,0,,There are times when people should laugh at it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.58,0:19:30.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, aren't you a dog?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.22,0:19:52.46,Default,,0,0,0,,What's up, Pace? Why have you stopped?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.09,0:19:56.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, get out of the way quickly!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.50,0:19:58.47,Default,,0,0,0,,The ship will come soon!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.51,0:20:08.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Here it is! It's Rory!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.07,0:20:10.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Oh! But...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.22,0:20:14.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Rory will cross the bridge!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.60,0:20:16.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn, the engine hangs now...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.29,0:20:22.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Rory!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.44,0:20:23.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, John!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.95,0:20:30.19,Default,,0,0,0,,You too, Dad! Run after the children!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.96,0:20:35.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey Pace!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.48,0:20:39.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to cross this bridge.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.33,0:20:43.85,Default,,0,0,0,,In the next village\Nwe will see beautiful things.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.03,0:20:52.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey come on, Pace!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.42,0:20:58.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Lassie?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.57,0:20:59.85,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.03,0:21:01.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh Doucho!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.71,0:21:05.68,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.75,0:21:07.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Rory, don't cross this bridge!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.28,0:21:10.49,Default,,0,0,0,,My father, it's my father's fault!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.73,0:21:12.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hey!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.58,0:21:14.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't go on that road!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.81,0:21:33.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.79,0:21:35.63,Default,,0,0,0,,This is because of these kids.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.18,0:21:39.35,Default,,0,0,0,,This means we will do\Nfun things there, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.25,0:21:44.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah! Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.83,0:22:02.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Sandy's poor cow was stolen.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.24,0:22:04.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We must find the perpetrator,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.65,0:22:07.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}so everyone decided to look for him.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.48,0:22:09.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Sandy behaves strangely!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.70,0:22:13.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Next episode:\NSANDY STEALS COWS?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.57,0:22:15.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Be sure to watch!{\i0}
